==French==
===Verb===
'''su''' {{m}} ({{f}} '''sue''', {{m}} {{p}} '''sus''', {{f}} {{p}} '''sues''')
# (''[[past participle]] of'' '''[[savoir]]''') [[known]] (''usually translated into English using the [[past tense]]'' (I knew) ''rather than the [[perfect tense]]'' (I have known))
